S"Find My Friends allows you and your friends to keep tabs on each other, even while apart. It\xe2\x80\x99s a great way to coordinate meet-ups, or regroup on a large outing.Find My Friends lets you:See the location of any friend or family member on a map, with their permission, through their cell phone - Find your friend\xe2\x80\x99s location for free on iPhone or Android. For any other phone, you get 3 free locations. Afterwards, it is $4.99 per month (we use triangulation data through the carriers so we share the cost with you).- Update locations on demand at any timeFind My Friends is the most accurate friend locator available for Android. Using the latest GPS tracking technology, Find My Friends will allow you to see friends on a private map, so you can know when they are nearby.  The app is the only friend locator on the market that will not drain your phone\xe2\x80\x99s battery. Find My Friends can also help you track lost or stolen phones! Use a friend\xe2\x80\x99s phone and locate the missing Android device. As long as the phone tracking app is running, you will be able to see the location of your lost or stolen phone, and will be able to launch navigation from within the app.Carriers who support the friend location app:If using the app on an Android phone or iPhone: All CarriersIf using another phone (US only): Verizon Wireless, Sprint, AT&T and T-MobileFriend location for iPhones and Android Phones:It\xe2\x80\x99s easy to get started. Download and install Find My Friends on your phone, create an account and invite your friends to do the same. As soon as your friends have joined your account, you can see their location on our Friend Location Map. For each person\xe2\x80\x99s profile, you can also see their location history, request a location update and check-in with your friends so they get your most updated location. If you or your friends need help, the panic button will let everyone know, along with providing the most recent location. This app is always free and works around the world (depending on your carrier).Friend location for other phones:Locating friends using other phones is even simpler. All you have to do is send your friend an invite via text message. All your friend has to do is text a \xe2\x80\x9cyes\xe2\x80\x9d reply. As soon as your friend accepts your invite, you can locate him or her instantly on our map with the push of a button. We use the same technology that you see on CSI or Law & Order referred to as \xe2\x80\x9ctriangulation.\xe2\x80\x9d Triangulation utilizes the cell phone carrier\xe2\x80\x99s network infrastructure to identify a cell phone\xe2\x80\x99s location. Because this data costs us money each time, we can only provide 3 free locations per account. Afterwards, you can upgrade to premium to receive unlimited locations for $4.99 per month. (Note: This premium feature only works in the US.)In the past, users have used the app to locate each other during:Traveling, Vacations, Theme parks (Disneyland, Disneyworld, Six Flags), Nightclubs, Clubbing, Bars, Parties, Street Fairs, Day Trips, Camping, Hiking, Skiing Trips, Las Vegas Trips, Shopping Malls, Sporting Events such as (Baseball Games, Football Games, Hockey Games, Nascar Races, Basketball Games, MLS Games, College Football Games, College Basketball Game Days, Game Days, Olympics, World Cup, Monster Truck Events), Going to the Park, Wine Trips, Sightseeing, Museums, Beach Trips, Food Fairs, Festivals, Nightlife, School, Concerts, Road Trips, Airport, Train Station, Zoo, Safari, Protest, Rally, Mardi Gras, Outside Lands, Coachella, Natural Disasters (Hurricanes, Flooding, Japan Earth Quake).Recent changes:- By popular request, we've added one-to-one messaging in your family chat channel- We have Increased location accuracy even further- And, as always, we've tackled a stack of bugs to give you a better overall experience"
